          <figure>
            要不是实在没有女孩子问津，谁会静下心来读书。 (<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/62941346/">查看原文</a>)

            <div class="blockquote-extra">
              <div class='blockquote-meta'>
                <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/low2han/" class="author-avatar">
                  <img width="20" height="20" src="https://img2.doubanio.com/icon/u2756419-2.jpg">
