      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">毕竟是十七岁少年写的，笔法相当拙劣。但鉴于其影响力，加一星。</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/1026425/?comment_id=428681435"></div>
    </div>
  </li>

          
